PrecisAppointment of the HONOURABLE WILLIAM J. VANCISE of Regina, Saskatchewan, to be part-time chairman of the Copyright Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, in the place of the Honourable John Howard Gomery, who has resigned.
